==English==

===Etymology===
Latin ''[[mundus]]''
===Adjective===
'''mundane''' pronounced ''mun'deyn''

# [[worldly]], [[profane]], as opposed to [[heavenly]]
# [[ordinary]]; not new
# [[tedious]]; repetitive and boring

====Synonyms====
*[[worldly]]
*[[routine]]


